   218â†’## 7.3.0
   219â†’
   220â†’* Add `subset(r1, r2)` method to determine if `r1` range is entirely
   221â†’  contained by `r2` range.
   222â†’
   223â†’## 7.2.3
   224â†’
   225â†’* Fix handling of `includePrelease` mode where version ranges like `1.0.0 -
   226â†’  2.0.0` would include `3.0.0-pre` and not `1.0.0-pre`.
   227â†’
   228â†’## 7.2.2
   229â†’
   230â†’* Fix bug where `2.0.0-pre` would be included in `^1.0.0` if
   231â†’  `includePrerelease` was set to true.
   232â†’
   233â†’## 7.2.0
   234â†’
   235â†’* Add `simplifyRange` method to attempt to generate a more human-readable
   236â†’  range expression that is equivalent to a supplied range, for a given set
   237â†’  of versions.
   238â†’
   239â†’## 7.1.2
   240â†’
   241â†’* Remove fancy lazy-loading logic, as it was causing problems for webpack
   242â†’  users.
   243â†’
   244â†’## 7.1.0
   245â†’
   246â†’* Add `require('semver/preload')` to load the entire module without using
   247â†’  lazy getter methods.
   248â†’
   249â†’## 7.0.0
   250â†’
   251â†’* Refactor module into separate files for better tree-shaking
   252â†’* Drop support for very old node versions, use const/let, `=>` functions,
   253â†’  and classes.
   254â†’
   255â†’## 6.3.0
   256â†’
   257â†’* Expose the token enum on the exports
   258â†’
   259â†’## 6.2.0
   260â†’
   261â†’* Coerce numbers to strings when passed to semver.coerce()
   262â†’* Add `rtl` option to coerce from right to left
   263â†’
   264â†’## 6.1.3
   265â†’
   266â†’* Handle X-ranges properly in includePrerelease mode
   267â†’
   268â†’## 6.1.2
   269â†’
   270â†’* Do not throw when testing invalid version strings
   271â†’
   272â†’## 6.1.1
   273â†’
   274â†’* Add options support for semver.coerce()
   275â†’* Handle undefined version passed to Range.test
   276â†’
   277â†’## 6.1.0
   278â†’
   279â†’* Add semver.compareBuild function
   280â†’* Support `*` in semver.intersects
   281â†’
   282â†’## 6.0
   283â†’
   284â†’* Fix `intersects` logic.
   285â†’
   286â†’    This is technically a bug fix, but since it is also a change to behavior
   287â†’    that may require users updating their code, it is marked as a major
   288â†’    version increment.
   289â†’
   290â†’## 5.7
   291â†’
   292â†’* Add `minVersion` method
   293â†’
   294â†’## 5.6
   295â†’
   296â†’* Move boolean `loose` param to an options object, with
   297â†’  backwards-compatibility protection.
   298â†’* Add ability to opt out of special prerelease version handling with
   299â†’  the `includePrerelease` option flag.
   300â†’
   301â†’## 5.5
   302â†’
   303â†’* Add version coercion capabilities
   304â†’
   305â†’## 5.4
   306â†’
   307â†’* Add intersection checking
   308â†’
   309â†’## 5.3
   310â†’
   311â†’* Add `minSatisfying` method
   312â†’
   313â†’## 5.2
   314â†’
   315â†’* Add `prerelease(v)` that returns prerelease components
   316â†’
   317â†’## 5.1
   318â†’
   319â†’* Add Backus-Naur for ranges
   320â†’* Remove excessively cute inspection methods
   321â†’
   322â†’## 5.0
